":"avg_npc_301_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太傅","text":"听着不差。","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_301_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_301_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"那就这么定，我先把酒温上。","id":45,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_301_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太傅","text":"......你倒很会做生意。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_301_1#4$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_301_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":48},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"做这行的，总归得有些眼力见儿。","id":49,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#8$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"您这样的老丈，没几个不爱多看看这尚蜀城的。就算不看城，也爱看人。","id":50,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#8$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_301_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太傅","text":"说的不错。","id":52,"figure":"avg_npc_301_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太傅","text":"人，确实当看，若不看人，就是白走一遭。","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_301_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太傅","text":"梁洵应当与你说过，他今晚便该随我回京。出尚蜀这趟路，便由你指引。","id":54,"figure":"avg_npc_301_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_301_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"......确实说过。","id":56,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"您别怪罪，梁大人这回走得急，我们这些人难免多担忧些。","id":57,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"我们这知府大人......说是了不得的父母官，可到底还年轻着呢，有时候看着就像家里的子侄，让人担心。","id":58,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_301_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太傅","text":"梁洵他有这般才能，也有志气。顶得住，便是功成名就。","id":60,"figure":"avg_npc_301_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_294_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_301_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老船夫","text":"要是顶不住呢？","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_294_1#1$1