pe":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"能在这山上坐坐，喝茶醒醒神，也不错。","id":121},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"这儿的茶点味道也挺好......油酥，芝麻糕，还有——","id":122},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"糖果子。","id":124},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"上回宁小姐夸奖过。","id":125},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":126},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"啊，您就记着了？","id":127},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":128},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"嗯。宁小姐喜欢，就多留意了些。","id":129},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":130},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"尚蜀什么都好，就是口味上有点重，好在糕点大多还是香软甜口的，合我的口味。","id":131},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"唉，梁大人府里煮的锅子最初也辣得很，之后倒好了不少。","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"最初动不了一筷子就要找水，太狼狈了。","id":134},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"府里解辣的汤时刻备着。","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"宁小姐的家乡......","id":137},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"南边水乡，不大吃辣。","id":139},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"难为你了。","id":141},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"这有什么，总归要适应的。","id":143},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"话虽如此，这不是轻易能做到的。","id":145},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"有心想要适应，就不难。","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"总归要适应的。","id":148},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":149},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......嗯。","id":150},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"梁大人之前提过，您是尚蜀本地人吧？","id":152},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"是。","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"梁某人早年离家，近些年才回到故乡。宁小姐知道的。","id":155},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"听你提起过。","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"这么说来，你的那位龙门朋友，就是在离家期间遇上的？","id":158},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"是的。","id":160},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"那时少不知事，离家闯荡，交了不少朋友，以为少年意气无坚不摧，无所不可为......","id":161},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":162},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"做了不少贻笑大方的蠢事。","id":163},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#10$1","focus":"1","id":164},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"交朋友可不算蠢事。","id":165},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"梁大人，你交的是位好朋友。","id":166},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":167},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......是梁某幸运。","id":168},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"要不是这次事出紧急，确实该好好请你那位朋友在尚蜀游览一番，尽一尽地主之谊。","id":170},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"还能多听两句梁大人的过往趣事，不知道同现在差别大不大。","id":171},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":172},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"我从未变过。","id":173},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":174},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"不......","id":175},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":176},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"或许还是有些变化。不过......","id":177},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"嗯？","id":179},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"梁某人要做的事，为一方百姓......从未变过。","id":181},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"......","id":183},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"昨夜太傅提出随他上京......我原本，不想应下。","id":185},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"你怪我替你答应了？","id":187},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"不。不会。","id":189},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"那时犹豫已经是不应该，我该谢谢宁小姐。","id":190},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"你不怪罪我就好了。你放心不下尚蜀，我能理解，其他人也能，但太傅开口是不一样的。","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"太傅身边不留庸才。他老人家给出的，只会是最险、最难搏的机会。","id":193},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"我想如果我没看错梁洵这个人，那你要是一时犹豫拒绝了，之后一定是会后悔的。","id":194},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......我明白。让宁小姐担心了。","id":196},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":197},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"......","id":198},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"......呵呵。","id":200},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":201},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"宁小姐......？","id":202},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":203},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"啊，没事，没什么。我只是忽然想到......","id":204},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":205},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"你那时要是当真毫不犹豫地同意要走，恐怕，我也是要有些生气的。","id":206},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":207},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......咳。宁小姐说笑了。","id":208},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":209},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"我可不是说笑。","id":210},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"咳咳咳。","id":212},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":213},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"这才多久，日头就起来了。","id":214},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":215},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"梁大人，这戏好看吗？","id":216},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":217},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"尚可。","id":218},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":219},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"那要不要早些下山？","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":221},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"不用。","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......再看一会。","id":223},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#10$1","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"宁小姐，再看一会。","id":226},{"type":"dialog","id":227},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":228},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":229},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g04_yaninn","screenadapt":"coverall","id":230},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$path_intro","key":"$path_loop","volume":"0.4","id":231,"musicid":1},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":232},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#1$1","fadetime":"0.5","id":233},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":234},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"好了好了，爹！别看了！","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"有什么啊，这有什么可看的，不就一张行程单嘛，我和其他人都商量好了，等东西收拾好了就出发！","id":236},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"我还有一屋子的东西没收拾呢！","id":238},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"急什么，我再看看......","id":240},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你们一群年轻人，决定做得那么急，容易出事。","id":242},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","focus":"1","id":243},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"年轻人怎么了？谁还不是从年轻时过来的，爹你年轻时不也天南地北地走镖？","id":244},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"能一样吗？","id":246},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"没人带着，你们晓得道上哪条路走得，哪条路走不得？","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"这时节出这么趟远门，你可知该带什么，不该带什么？","id":248},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"爹！","id":250},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"时代不同了爹，可别翻您那老黄历了！","id":251},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":252},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"遥夜！听话，爹能给你说的不多了，这次......","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你定了要去玉门城，就去吧。我也拦不住你们，不走我们给铺的这条路，没准也是好事......","id":254},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"......","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"爹啊，假如说啊，我就打个比方......","id":257},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":258},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"假如我们这客栈不开了，您还有几个叔伯，有没有考虑过和我们一起去玉门城？","id":259},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":260},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......遥夜啊......","id":261},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"哎爹我就随口说说，我晓得肯定不成的！您就随便听听......","id":263},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"遥夜。","id":265},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"......哎。","id":267},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"这客栈本来就是为你留的，你要是不接手，趁早歇业关门也好。","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你说要自立门户，我不拦着，我信你是有考虑的，但我还是得给你说两句，你也别嫌爹啰嗦。","id":270},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","focus":"1","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"爹......","id":272},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你给年轻人们牵了头，他们都信你，跟着你，你说时代变了......没错，时代是变了，但这事放在什么时候都变不了。","id":274},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你既然站出来，一呼百应，那往后遇上再难的事，你也不能退，再苦，再累，你得担着，听见没有？","id":275},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"......","id":277},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"我知道。","id":278},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":279},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"我......知道的，爹。","id":280},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":281},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"......唉。行了，这单子你拿去，有些不那么好走的路，我给你避开些，能走大道便走大道，那些我们蹚过的泥巴路，你们可别再踩。","id":282},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"您放心。","id":284},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"放心，难啊。","id":286},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"我现在就有桩心事。","id":287},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","focus":"1","id":288},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"您说。","id":289},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":290},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"遥夜，你年纪也不小了，这次去玉门城，能不能正经带个小伙子回来看看......","id":291},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","focus":"1","id":292},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"15","times":"1","fadetime":"0.3","block":"false","id":293},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"停，停！！","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"爹！瞎操什么心呢！！","id":295},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"怎么是瞎操心了？","id":297},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":298},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"这就是瞎操心！","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"哎呀，不同爹你说了，我还要去一趟梁大人府里......","id":300},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"你找梁大人作甚？","id":302},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":303},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"不是我要找，是那个姓鲤的要找！","id":304},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","focus":"2","id":305},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"他都找不着，可见梁大人应当不在府里，你去又有什么用？","id":306},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_296_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","focus":"1","id":307},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"杜小姐","text":"......有道理。好啊，这姓鲤的又用这招糊弄我！我现在就去找他算账！","id":308},{"type":"Dialog","id":309},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#3$1","fadetime":"1","id":310},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","id":311},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":312},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"avg_npc_300_1#2$1","focus":"2","id":313},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"唉......","id":314},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":315},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"郑掌柜","text":"姑娘家家的，什么时候才能稳重些哦......","id":316},{"type":"dialog","id":317},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":318},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":319},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":320},{"type":"playMusic","key":"$midautumn","volume":"0.4","id":321,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":322},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":323},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":324},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"别人的家事，不要东张西望。","id":325},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":326},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......不用操心。","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"麟青砚，你现在这是什么意思？","id":328},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":329},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"吃饭。","id":330},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你知道我不是问这个。","id":332},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"你一早就等在这里，阻拦我去见那三位，总得给我一个理由。","id":333},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":334},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"我说过，我会同你一起去。","id":335},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":336},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"麟青砚！","id":337},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#3$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":338},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"大呼小叫，像什么样子。","id":339},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"我并非代表大理寺走这一趟，不论官职，你该叫我什么？","id":340},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":341},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":342},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#5$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"规矩你是忘了？","id":344},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......小姨。","id":346},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":347},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"嗯。","id":348},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":349},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"何必总搬出这一套来压我？又不是什么正经的亲戚，你也不过是仗着麟家和我爹相交，长我一个辈分......","id":350},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"天师府这次要你走这一趟，到底为了什么？","id":351},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":352},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"自然是为百姓苍生。","id":353},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":354},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"好一个为百姓苍生。","id":355},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"既然如此，真就要放任......真就这么继续下去？","id":356},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":357},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"太傅已经做下判断，我等遵令即可。","id":358},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"倒是你，左乐。","id":359},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":360},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":361},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":362},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"你入司岁台时日尚浅，这次尚蜀背后所藏之事不简单，现在看来，许多内幕你并不知情......","id":363},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"当差却一知半解，荒唐！谁叫你来的？","id":364},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":365},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......无人指派，是我主动请缨。","id":366},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":367},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"怎么，你不相信？","id":368},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#6$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":369},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"我信。","id":370},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"我信你主动请缨，却也信有人背后作怪。","id":371},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":372},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......我倒是头一次听说，大理寺铁面无私忠直坦白的麟青砚，也学会揣测这些官场阴私了。","id":373},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"传闻里你不是最厌烦理会这类蝇营狗苟，要是有人与你聒噪，就要电他个顶盖发麻？","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"如今这样，可不是你的风格。","id":375},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":376},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"我的行事风格，不必你提点。","id":377},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"我被托付关照你，事关你，自然应当谨慎些。","id":378},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":379},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......啧。","id":380},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":381},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"你弹舌？","id":382},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":383},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"没有的事，小姨听错了。","id":384},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":385},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"......","id":386},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"待此间事了，你也该同我回一趟京城。","id":387},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":388},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"可......","id":389},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"2","id":390},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"惊蛰","text":"这是左将军的意思。","id":391},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":392},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"......","id":393},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_297_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_039_1","focus":"1","id":394},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"左乐","text":"知道了。我随你回去。","id":395},{"type":"dialog","id":396},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":397},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":398},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g09_teahouse","screenadapt":"coverall","id":399},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","id":400},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":401},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":402},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"礼部左侍郎......其实是个不太参与政务的职位。","id":403},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"梁大人有没有听说过，我如今这官职是怎么来的？","id":404},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":405},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"愿闻其详。","id":406},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":407},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"梁大人靠自己出人头地，这是我比不上的。","id":408},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"宁家......算是个大姓。祖上蒙荫，后人也算上进，一辈辈积累些门路财产，就这么传下来。","id":409},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"我祖父官至一品，勤勤恳恳几十年，就是我不说名字，梁大人应该也认得。","id":410},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":411},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......","id":412},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":413},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"也就是对着梁大人，我才肯说，不然这话显得像是我要炫耀。","id":414},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":415},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"不会。","id":416},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":417},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"宁小姐......很好。","id":418},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":419},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"我知道你不会这么想。","id":420},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"之前也和梁大人说过，我在家中同辈的兄弟姐妹里行七。","id":421},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":422},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"嗯。","id":423},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":424},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"我父亲那一辈人志不在此，小辈们也是，我最大的堂兄大我十来岁，早已成家立业。","id":425},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"祖父准备从官场上退下时，正巧我年少气盛，被卷进一个走私贪污的案子，侥幸抓了一串贼人，转天公文就被送到祖父案头。","id":426},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":427},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"宁小姐才干过人。","id":428},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":429},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"场面话。","id":430},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":431},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"不敢。是真心话。","id":432},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":433},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"那我信你。","id":434},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":435},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"祖父那时候单独将我喊去书房，我们没聊什么特别的，他老人家就问了我一个问题。","id":436},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"他问：“辞秋，你这一身才学本领，可愿为国、为民、为天下？”","id":437},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"我就答说......","id":438},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":439},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......肝脑涂地。","id":440},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":441},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"在所不辞。","id":442},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#7$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":443},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"宁小姐好气魄。","id":444},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":445},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"好啦，故事就讲到这里。","id":446},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"梁大人，茶凉了。","id":447},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#9$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":448},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"还有些温度。","id":449},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":450},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"可我看梁大人你的手已凉了。要是你乐意我将这披风还你一半，我们倒也不是不能再沏上一壶热茶。","id":451},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":452},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......身体要紧，披好，别摘了。","id":453},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":454},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"我没事，不信你试试......是不是比你梁洵暖和？","id":455},{"type":"Dialog","id":456},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","id":457},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"50","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":458},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_avg_clothmovement","volume":"0.6","id":459},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":460},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"0.8","block":"true","id":461},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":462},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#1$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":463},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"梁某人手冷，别冻着宁小姐。","id":464},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"12","ystrength":"13","vibrato":"15","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":465},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":466},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"哎呀！","id":467},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":468},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"今天之后，不知要什么时候才有机会再见。","id":469},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#1$1","focus":"2","id":470},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"宁小姐要多保重身体，不要贪凉。","id":471},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......要是......","id":472},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"2","id":473},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"要是宁小姐往后还要赏花，不嫌路途遥远，便不必自己动手，托人带一封信，交给我来种就是。","id":474},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#8$1","focus":"1","id":475},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"......","id":476},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#8$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#9$1","focus":"2","id":477},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"宁小姐？","id":478},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#4$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":479},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"哎，啊，嗯......","id":480},{"type":"Dialog","id":481},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":482},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#2$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":483},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"嗯......你既然都这样说了，那我就也直说了。","id":484},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#9$1","focus":"1","id":485},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"梁大人，你兜里那扎了缎带的首饰盒子，还要揣多久？","id":486},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":487},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"梁洵","text":"......咳，这是......","id":488},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_298_1#10$1","name2":"avg_npc_295_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":489},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"是什么？","id":490},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"宁小姐","text":"怎么，梁大人，难不成那还能是你准备要送给旁人的？","id":491},{"type":"dialog","id":492},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":493},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":494},{"type":"Background","image":"25_g06_mountainroad_d","screenadapt":"coverall","id":495},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2.5","block":"true","id":496},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":497},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":498},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"......","id":499,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"顶唔顺啊。","id":500,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":501},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"......不该带你来找人。","id":502,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","id":503},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太合","text":"不该。","id":504,"figure":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1","id":505},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"太合","text":"你不露面？","id":506,"figure":"avg_npc_299_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#2$1","id":507},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"现在露面，不合适吧。","id":508,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#2$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","id":509},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"他们这你来我往，简直比台上的戏还精彩。","id":510,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"谁想到这姓梁的......唉，算了。","id":511,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#5$1","id":512},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"......不，不行，不能算了！","id":513,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#5$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"谁想到这姓梁的，十多年未见，成如今这样！","id":514,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1","id":515},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"挑山人","text":"十多年未见，不稀奇。","id":516,"figure":"avg_npc_302_1#1$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#5$1","id":517},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"难顶。","id":518,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#5$1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1","id":519},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"好在还有茶可喝，有戏可看。","id":520,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"这么一来，梁洵啊，你可是又欠我一笔。","id":521,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":522},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":523},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_322_lmlee_1#9$1","id":524},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"唉......","id":525,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"老鲤","text":"想找老朋友喝最后一杯酒，到底是难咯。","id":526,"figure":"avg_322_lmlee_1#9$1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":527},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":528},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":529},{"type":"Character","id":530}],"characters":["老船夫","？？？","太傅","宁小姐","梁洵","杜小姐","郑掌柜","左乐","惊蛰","老鲤","挑山人","太合"]}